name: We Do What We Must 03
description:
Each "Strange Beauty" OBJKT I curate is the dream of a GAN or Generative Adversarial Network: two AIs locked in competition, one a trained expert in detecting what an image depicts (dog, cat, car, etc.) and the other pitted against it in an effort to learn to FOOL the first.

Each Strange Beauty AI Curation will be minted only once.
